sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: Browser intercepts the form submission event and prevents page reload
    browser->>browser: e.preventDefault() (Prevents page reload)

    Note right of browser: The note is added to the list and the UI is updated
    browser->>browser: notes.push(note)
    browser->>browser: redrawNotes() (Updates the interface)

    Note right of browser: Browser sends the new note to the server via AJAX
    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Acknowledgment response (201 Created)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The new note is now stored on the server, and the UI reflects the changes
